<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="12Jun1938"><font color="red">12 June 1938</font> <i>NLGC</i> (from Maurice Craig to JJ): I have also written today to Mr Sam Henry about &ldquo;The Lord in his Mercy&rdquo;. He will probably be able to let you have it, tune and all. </div>
